    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="物理层扩展以太网"><a href="#物理层扩展以太网" class="headerlink" title="物理层扩展以太网"></a>物理层扩展以太网</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201506688.png" alt="image-20220320150617564"></p><ul><li>主机和集线器之间超过100m会严重丢帧。</li></ul><h2 id="物理层扩展以太网-1"><a href="#物理层扩展以太网-1" class="headerlink" title="物理层扩展以太网"></a>物理层扩展以太网</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201508558.png" alt="image-20220320150824428"></p><ul><li>缺点：通信效率变低，冲突概率变高。</li></ul><h1 id="链路层扩展以太网"><a href="#链路层扩展以太网" class="headerlink" title="链路层扩展以太网"></a>链路层扩展以太网</h1><h2 id="网桥"><a href="#网桥" class="headerlink" title="网桥"></a>网桥</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201510324.png" alt="image-20220320151040176"></p><h3 id="网桥的分类"><a href="#网桥的分类" class="headerlink" title="网桥的分类"></a>网桥的分类</h3><h4 id="透明网桥"><a href="#透明网桥" class="headerlink" title="透明网桥"></a>透明网桥</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201511560.png" alt="image-20220320151154419"></p><h4 id="源路由网桥"><a href="#源路由网桥" class="headerlink" title="源路由网桥"></a>源路由网桥</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201514198.png" alt="image-20220320151414059"></p><h2 id="交换机"><a href="#交换机" class="headerlink" title="交换机"></a>交换机</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201516166.png" alt="image-20220320151646022"></p><h3 id="两种交换方式"><a href="#两种交换方式" class="headerlink" title="两种交换方式"></a>两种交换方式</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201518372.png" alt="image-20220320151807236"></p><h1 id="冲突域与广播域"><a href="#冲突域与广播域" class="headerlink" title="冲突域与广播域"></a>冲突域与广播域</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201519941.png" alt="image-20220320151919802"></p><h2 id="例题"><a href="#例题" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201521968.png" alt="image-20220320152132826"></p><ul><li>广播域就是看有几个集线器。</li><li>冲突域看交换机有几个口。</li></ul><h1 id="脑图时刻"><a href="#脑图时刻" class="headerlink" title="脑图时刻"></a>脑图时刻</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203201524617.png" alt="image-20220320152428494"></p>]]></content>
    
    
